        <div class="container" id="servicesStrip">
            <h1 class="display-4">Services</h1>
            <p>Whether you just want a quick and cheap Wordpress site or you want to go all out for a bespoke but still affordable custom website, I've got you covered, just drop me a message to get an exact quote for what you want.</p>
            <br><br>
            <table class="table text-center">
                <tbody>
                    <tr>
                    <th scope="row">Website Design</th>
                    <td>Using Wordpress I can create a fully responsive and mobile-friendly website for you</td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                    <th scope="row">Bespoke Website Development</th>
                    <td>Whatever you need I can code it for you, Using HTML, CSS, JAVA, PHP and MYSQL Databases I can create the custom website you need from Blogs to Social networks to E-commerce sites for your business, whatever you need I can make it fully responsive and mobile-friendly!</td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                    <th scope="row">Website Hosting / Domains and Email Accounts</th>
                    <td>When I code your custom website for you I can either hand the source code over to you to do with as you wish or I can get it online for you and set you up with your own .com/.co.uk domain and an appropriate business email address so you can contact customers looking as professional as possible.</td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                    <th scope="row">Website Content Management</th>
                    <td>If I or someone else coded a website for you and you want something changed on it I can get the job done quickly, also if you just need someone to keep the content on your website up to date and fresh then I can do it all for a low hourly fee.</td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                    <th scope="row">SEO Management</th>
                    <td>With the amount of people using the internet today, if you want to reach your target audience you need to apply Search Engine Optimization (SEO) techniques so that you rank first on google, you may have no idea where to start but don't worry I've got you covered!</td>
                    </tr>
                </tbody>
            </table>
